2. **`unique_signers`** — prevents duplicate entries in the datum inflating the apparent quorum
3. **`all_present`** — the core check via `all_signed`, now explicitly named for clarity
4. **`sufficient_signatories`** — double-checks the transaction carries at least as many signatures as required, providing a redundant sanity guard
